  "remarks": "The Institute of Applied Physics provides research and development for Iran’s nuclear programme. It has project partnerships with the EU-listed Organisation of Defensive Innovation and Research (SPND), which is a subsidiary of EU-listed Ministry of Defense for Armed Forces Logistics (MODAFL), working to weaponise the nuclear programme, which is under the authority of the General Staff of the Armed Forces.",
